latestPosts.caption:
My top Beauty Secrets👇🏼🤫

1. Double Cleansing: 

I use the @elemis_india Pro Collagen balm cleanser (liquid cleansers are too messy) followed up with @skin1004_india Centella pore cleansing face wash (ALWAYS follow with a soap based cleanser).

2. Daily Sunscreen (not why you think): 

We know the UV rays reason, but I religiously use it to prevent hyperpigmentation as I use Vitamin C in the morning. If you are using actives, you are more prone to skin burns, protect your skin barrier. I use @mywishcare 

3. Use the RIGHT body moisturiser: 

Stop picking the random, cheap body moisturisers and search according to your skin type. I have Keratosis Pilaris and my go to is @firstaidbeauty 

Drop your beauty secrets in the comments, I am always looking for more tips!
